11:00 12:30  NETWORKS
<P>
Security Flaws in the HotJava Web Browser
Drew Dean, Dan S. Wallach
<P>
On Two Proposals for On-line Credit-card Payments using Open
Networks: Problems and Solutions
Wenbo Man
<P>
