Ravi Iyer, U. of Illinois, USA
Karama Kanoun, LAAS-CNRS, France
Carl E. Landwehr, Naval Res. Lab., USA
Jean-Claude Laprie, LAAS-CNRS, France
Bev Littlewood, City U. London, Great Britain
