DeFazio (D-OR), Timothy Johnson (D-SD), Bernard Sanders (independent-VT)
<P>
Senators
<P>
Dianne Feinstein (D-CA), Patrick Leahy (D-VT), Paul Simon (D-IL), Paul
Wellstone (D-MN), Russ Feingold (D-WI), and John McCain (R-AZ).
