<DT><IMG SRC="/Images/redball.gif" ALT="o" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="14">
<A HREF="#subj10">Re: RISKS of typing credit-card numbers</A>
<DD><A HREF="#subj10.1">Nathaniel Borenstein</A><BR>
<A HREF="#subj10.2">Olin Sibert</A><BR>
