&gt; though, the mail will be accepted for delivery.  If you have legitimate<BR>
&gt; mail, it will eventually get through (many messages from the same<BR>
&gt; correspondent will be flushed without acknowledgement).  However,<BR>
&gt; correspondents who were used to getting a reply within seconds telling them<BR>
&gt; that their message was accepted may see a substantial delay.<BR>
