<H3><A NAME="subj12.1">The Second USENIX Workshop on Electronic Commerce: cfp</A></H3>
<ADDRESS>
Bennet Yee
&lt;<A HREF="mailto:bsy@Play.UCSD.Edu">bsy@Play.UCSD.Edu</A>&gt;
</ADDRESS>
<I>Sat, 6 Apr 1996 14:58:35 -0800</I><PRE>

